features: ❶Enhanced Gaming Experience: The TRIMUI SMART PRO game console features a bright 4.96-inch display with 720*1280 resolution, providing vivid details for an enhanced gaming experience. Its long-lasting 5000 mAh battery ensures up to 5 hours of playtime

❷Superior Operating System: Equipped with a Allwinner A133P (A133 Plus) 1.8GHz high-performance processor, this game console offers improved running speed and higher stability, providing a smooth and seamless gaming experience

❸Extensive Game Library: With support for over 12700 classic games, the TRIMUI SMART PRO covers a wide range of genres including adventure, shooting, action, racing, and arcade games. Enjoy endless hours of fun and nostalgia with this console

❹Portable and Convenient: Designed with a compact and lightweight body, this handheld console is ultra-portable and perfect for gaming on the go. Take it with you wherever you are and enjoy your favorite games anytime, anywhere

❺Complete Package: The package includes everything you need to start gaming right away, including 1 x TRIMUI SMART PRO Game Console (Black), 1 x TRIMUI SMART PRO Case, 1 x Charging Cable, 1 x 128G Game Card
